*Sistema* je automatizovana, tako da je sve lakše i brže. (The system is automated, so everything is easier and faster.)

Kompanija je implementirala novu *sistemu*. (The company has implemented a new system.)

*Sistema* podrške je veoma korisna za korisnike. (The support system is very useful for users.)

*Sistema* obrazovanja je u fazi modernizacije. (The education system is in the process of modernization.)

Softver je usklađen sa modernom *sistemom*. (The software is aligned with the modern system.)